能你無睇live，我summarize下<br />\n<br />\n今晚有一大堆貌似勇武既人係大街(有口罩但唔係full gear)(黃金麥記對開)<br />\n隔百幾米係防暴，之後鴨寮街(小路)係有d街坊/花生友係附近，大量記者都係度<br />\n正常諗，防暴係會等緊清大街既人<br />\n但點知d狗係突然發難，衝入鴨寮街，好多人都係走唔切，好多都無口罩，就咁拉哂...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8a7a07980e5af5a8271be9e456c82b05566015","tid":1425683,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:09:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dc4aeb8ace70d9a376910976845738a68061c14","tid":1425683,"uid":70878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:13:57.000Z","msg":"其實佢地打緊民意戰<br />\n特登製造混亂場面<br />\n等傳媒影到"},{"pid":"f10750554f147556fdf4dd30c03eb33dd123c57c","tid":1425683,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:16:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"727aa03da1016fa6d41b0443a5764e4b5a6b6151","tid":1425683,"uid":168911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3dc4aeb8ace70d9a376910976845738a68061c14","tid":1425683,"uid":70878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:13:57.000Z","msg":"其實佢地打緊民意戰<br />\n特登製造混亂場面<br />\n等傳媒影到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:18:08.000Z","msg":"都係一點，比中間派睇，反送中累及無辜<br />\n遲下唔知會唔會，影住小朋友喊住話後悔參加反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似大陸咁電視認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33feebe261fb22b88b559d81bdabd51db00e7891","tid":1425683,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:20:30.000Z","msg":"集思廣益 push"},{"pid":"d0282fd96cfd7c75eb20e84762d4f1cfd9e11d30","tid":1425683,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:25:21.000Z","msg":"如果真係有人怪勇武搞到有人比人拉呢個諗法都幾離譜,明明係警犬亂咬人又燒返落勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54d7b62a9e396e16d1009cf243b318782176b25","tid":1425683,"uid":276110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0282fd96cfd7c75eb20e84762d4f1cfd9e11d30","t